{"tid":617661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本高鐵專家轟中國輕視安全","createTime":"2018-04-05T06:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T07:45:29.000Z","uid":70063,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f19a7a8c3cd14c62d040b83f0d854b3eef0fe8b7","tid":617661,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"高鐵獲官媒吹捧為「中國新四大發明」之一，總里程已達上萬公里，堪稱世界第一，成為中共對外炫耀的成就，更對外推銷。事實上，自從高鐵開建以來就不斷傳出負面消息，安全受到嚴重質疑，早年更遭日本專家批評「輕視安全、速度臨界」。<br />\n<br />\n高鐵工程師：決不坐<br />\n<br />\n2011年的溫州動車墮橋慘劇，高速鐵路D3115次「和諧號」動車在浙江溫州追尾相撞，部份車廂從橋上墜落，造成最少40死，近200傷，令中國鐵路安全受嚴重質疑。惟中共官方堅稱肇事和諧號只屬動車，圖與高鐵劃清界線。此前，官方《人民日報》陝西分社社長杜峻曾撰文指，有參與修建高鐵的工程師斷言「這輩子出門決不會坐高鐵，也勸親友不坐高鐵」，因為知道高鐵有太多安全隱患。<br />\n<br />\n日本新幹線2006年曾為中國生產高鐵車廂，設計最高時速是315公里，設定最高時速則為250公里，不過兩年後中方擅自大幅提速，超越東日本鐵道公司JR技術合作範圍，曾為中國高鐵生產車廂的日本JR東海董事長葛西敬之批評「中國高鐵輕視安全、速度臨界，改良的技術也是盜用外國」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171115/20214770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F20214770&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0Ljr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=1a39ff32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F20214770&h=59bb85f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171115/20214770</a>"},{"pid":"abd00dd6ea9096b05853b4d84c7267e5017b7c02","tid":617661,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96df051b2f22c98d7b771da9898226187b9ad5dd","tid":617661,"uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abd00dd6ea9096b05853b4d84c7267e5017b7c02","tid":617661,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"設計 施工 監管「一條龍」造假 高鐵貴州段揭豆腐渣<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171115/20214763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F20214763&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0Ljr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d49191b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F20214763&h=766e03ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171115/20214763</a>"},{"pid":"44ee46e3c060a3b6c075e9034043fbf273164730","tid":617661,"uid":31261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"abd00dd6ea9096b05853b4d84c7267e5017b7c02","tid":617661,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"冇定冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ce5e0e3733cef76ec042bc4910059796816f61","tid":617661,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>近年都無發生大事</blockquote><br />\n冇定冇人知&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n都有發生大事，未有人受傷或致命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81c91106b24e8435176bf8cf6eddc7afa6d21be","tid":617661,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abd00dd6ea9096b05853b4d84c7267e5017b7c02","tid":617661,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"無報道就無問題，即係無事啦"},{"pid":"3a2d1cd121f3c6333f1b04e98da597d9fb0b927e","tid":617661,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b296cd40d4cf4932808208450903859c05ab8481","